{"tid":1454120,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］滙豐一周3高層離職 亞太區首席風險官今年底前退休","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T23:22:53.000Z","uid":26418,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0c62805d437d9b28455d86c6a32fbd0e8bf683fd","tid":1454120,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:15:47.000Z","msg":"滙豐(00005)再有高層離職，滙豐亞太區首席風險官Mark McKeown將於今年底前退休，Ed Jenkins將接任其職，9月起生效。<br />\n<br />\n外電引述滙豐發言人指，今年4月已得悉Mark McKeown的退休計劃，他離職與已辭任的大中華區行政總裁黃碧娟、以及行政總裁范寧(John Flint)無關，亦與華為和中國沒有關係。 Mark McKeown於1976年加入滙豐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2424495?r=cpstni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2424495%3Fr%3Dcpstni&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=03a9e676\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2424495?r=cpstni</a>"},{"pid":"88852b01227d6df1f86e47f70623c3aec4c368db","tid":1454120,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c688061000185450a9a3927d8b4aed0af98f359","tid":1454120,"uid":26418,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"唔敢想像年尾經濟有幾差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3434aaae3b67217ca986ad7c2035806203a4118f","tid":1454120,"uid":60150,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"退休同埋之前兩者辭職唔同"},{"pid":"b2dd2428c5a8ca38854bd5f93c0008b26fd5faf8","tid":1454120,"uid":12609,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"即係另外兩個同華為同中國有關啦"},{"pid":"ce91dfe7693e11e9f0f3917deb004b46be98fc58","tid":1454120,"uid":237528,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12